.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, lemonade, sprite
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, scooter, bike
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, singing, writing
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, canadian, nigerian
1. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1
4. the australian is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person driving the bike is between the nigerian and the person driving the roller##2
7. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the canadian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | lemonade | cola       | sprite   |
| Transport          | roller   | bike   | scooter     |
| Hobby         | singing  | puzzles    | writing  |
| Nationality   | canadian | australian | nigerian |

