There 3 different types of food: eggplant, kale, spinach
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, classical, d&b
City: nizza, boston, hannover
1. the person eating spinach is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
3. the person traveling to boston is the person traveling to boston##1
4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person eating kale##1
5. the fan of classical is the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person traveling to nizza and the person traveling to boston##2
7. the fan of d&b is the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage      | water     | soy-milk | lemonade  |
| Food          | spinach   | kale     | eggplant  |
| Music-Genre   | d&b       | blues    | classical |
| City   | nizza | hannover     | boston   |

