3 different games are played: canasta, go, bridge
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person playing canasta##2
2. the person drinking mirinda is the person watching sports movies##1
3. the person playing go is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person watching animation movies is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
7. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |
| Beverage      | coffee    | fanta        | mirinda |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | martial-arts | sports  |
| Sport         | handball  | biathlon     | surfing |
| Game     | canasta      | bridge   | go    |

