.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, mirinda
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, musician, pilot
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, comedy, fantasy
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, car, tram
1. the pilot is on the left of the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
4. the dancer is on the far left##1
5. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
7. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
8. the person watching comedy movies is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |       3       |
| Beverage      | mirinda | juice  | hot-chocolate |
| Job           | dancer  | pilot  | musician      |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | comedy | animation     |
| Transport           | tram  | motorbike | car         |

 